"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Spanish passengers were the first to leave the MV Hondius after an outbreak where three people died and several got sick. A special team went to Tristan da Cunha, a remote British territory, to help them.\",            \"english_title\": \"Spanish Passengers Leave Ship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Pasajeros espa\u00f1oles fueron los primeros en salir del MV Hondius despu\u00e9s de un brote donde murieron tres personas y varias se enfermaron. Un equipo especial fue a Tristan da Cunha, un territorio brit\u00e1nico remoto, para ayudarlos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pasajeros Espa\u00f1oles Salen del Barco\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Spanish national Saif Abu Keshek and Brazilian Thiago \u00c1vila were arrested by Israel after they sailed in a flotilla carrying aid to Gaza.\",            \"english_title\": \"Arrest of Activists\",            \"translated_version\": \"El espa\u00f1ol Saif Abu Keshek y el brasile\u00f1o Thiago \u00c1vila fueron arrestados por Israel despu\u00e9s de navegar en una flotilla con ayuda para Gaza.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Arresto de Activistas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Celebrities, filmmakers, and creators performed at Africa's biggest night of film and fashion.\",            \"english_title\": \"Africa's Film and Fashion Night\",            \"translated_version\": \"Celebridades, cineastas y creadores actuaron en la noche m\u00e1s grande de cine y moda de \u00c1frica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Noche de Cine y Moda en \u00c1frica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Russian leader sees a chance for talks with Ukraine but criticizes the West for supporting President Zelensky.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Leader on Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El l\u00edder ruso ve una oportunidad para hablar con Ucrania pero critica a Occidente por apoyar al Presidente Zelensky.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edder Ruso sobre Conversaciones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Officials are looking into what caused an incident at a popular marina in southern Florida.\",            \"english_title\": \"Incident in Florida Marina\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los oficiales est\u00e1n investigando qu\u00e9 caus\u00f3 un incidente en una marina popular en el sur de Florida.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente en Marina de Florida\"        }    ]}"